--- Loi giai chi tiet phan (b) ---
Ma tran kiem tra H (2x4):
1 0 1 1 
0 1 1 0 
1. Phan tich khong gian nghiem cua H...
   Do dai ma (n): 4
   So chieu ma (k): 2
2. Sinh tat ca 2^k = 4 tu ma...
3. Tap day du cac tu ma:
   0000
   0111
   1001
   1110
Ket luan: Da sinh thanh cong 4 tu ma.
